\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 \ul \ulc0 Torque Tracer
\b0\fs24 \ulnone \
\pard\pardeftab720
\cf0 \
This program was developed to ease data entry for {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://vdrift.net"}}{\fldrslt VDrift}} a great cross-platform, open source driving simulation made with drift racing in mind.\
\

